ie, X., The effects of volcanism on the Permo-Triassic mass extinction in South China (1992) Permo-Triassic Events in the Eastern Tethys, pp. 146-157. , Cambridge University Press, Cambridge, W.C. Sweet, Z. Yang, J.M. Dickins, H. Yin (Eds.); Yin, H., Sweet, W.C., Glenister, B.F., Kotlyar, G., Kozur, H., Newell, N.D., Sheng, J., Zakharov, Y.D., Recommendation of the Meishan section as Global Stratotype Section and Point for basal boundary of Triassic System (1996) Newsletters on Stratigraphy, 34 (2), pp. 81-108; Yin, H., Wu, S., Ding, M., Zhang, K., Tong, J., Yang, F., Lai, X., The Meishan section, candidate of the global stratotype section and point of Permian-Triassic boundary (1996) Candidates of Global Stratotype Section and Point of the Permian-Triassic Boundary, pp. 31-48. , China University of Geosciences Press, H. Yin (Ed.) NSFC Project No. 49472087. The Palaeozoic-Mesozoic boundary; Yin, H., Zhang, K., Wu, S., Peng, Y., Global correlation and definition of the Permian-Triassic boundary (1996) Candidates of Global Stratotype Section and Point of the Permian-Triassic Boundary, pp. 3-28. , China University of Geosciencs Press, Wuhan, H. Yin (Ed.) The Palaeozoic-Mesozoic boundary; Yin, H., Zhang, K., Tong, J., Yang, Z., Wu, S., The Global Stratotype Section and Point (GSSP) of the Permian-Triassic boundary (2001) Episodes, 24 (2), pp. 102-114; Yin, H., Tong, J., Zhang, K., A review on the Global Stratotype Section and Point of the Permian-Triassic boundary (2005) Acta Geologica Sinica, 79 (6), pp. 715-728; Yin, H., Feng, Q., Lai, X., Baud, A., Tong, J., The protracted Permo-Triassic crisis and multi-episode exticntion around the Permian-Triassic boundary (2007) Global and Planetary Change, 55, pp. 1-20; Yin, H., Yang, F., Yu, J., Peng, Y., Wang, S., Zhang, S., An accurately delineated Permian-Triassic boundary in continental successions (2007) Science in China Series D: Earth Sciences, 50 (9), pp. 1281-1292","Kozur, H.W.Rézsü u. 83, H-1029 Budapest, Hungary; ema